    interview:example "User types 'fac' -> lookup trie node for 'fac' -> return top 10 children by score; Background: aggregate logs -> update trie with popular queries; Cache: Redis stores prefix -> suggestions mapping; Ranking: frequency * recency * personalization score" ;
