    interview:keyPoints "Requirements: collect metrics, store timeseries data, query/visualize, alerting; Components: collection agents, ingestion API, timeseries DB (Prometheus, InfluxDB), aggregation service, query API, visualization, alerting engine; Data model: metric name + labels + timestamp + value; Scale: pre-aggregation, downsampling, retention policies, sharding by metric; Alerting: rule engine, notification channels; Consider: high cardinality, compression, retention tiers" ;
